{"tid":269130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中介團隊 同 蔣介石 入黎","createTime":"2017-06-03T14:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T15:09:32.000Z","uid":82543,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03af0e661af51e7280da1723a031831d67ccbe0f","tid":269130,"uid":82543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"你地2邊咪撚煩日鳩日開埋堆垃圾post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中介果邊又係傻鳩黎 佢癲你地又陪佢癲 蔣狗上網鳩up下你估真係影響到你生意咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你果間麻辣唔知咩春 真心難食 又貴 <br />\n好心review下堆產品質素 <br />\n你請埋網絡打手又係無撚腦<br />\n本生撚佢幾野 隻蔣狗已經發哂癲 無人理<br />\n你地又係咁追擊 引人記得返中介單野<br />\n貼出黎屌蔣狗堆野 好小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話咩非禮 但證據就係對話圖<br />\n老老實實 呢堆野我去鴨記是撚旦買幾張太空卡 已經整到<br />\n加上 係咪唔夠ac 我見幾個post黎黎去去都係果幾個user <br />\n<br />\n蔣狗又係傻鳩黎 個樣生得搞笑唔再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開波追擊中介係幾好睇 之後走火入魔<br />\n成個傻鳩咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比人撚2撚 又亂鳩咁up<br />\nEq 好撚低 <br />\n<br />\n總括：2邊都係傻鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3416520328d767b579172de814d818a947e5ebb2","tid":269130,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:21:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5472c697f8d24b8e1db6c9752d694d149dc823a2","tid":269130,"uid":82543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當笑話睇啫</blockquote><br />\n好春煩 3日唔埋就見到"},{"pid":"55d836312980ded16c4a30e1670272fc97880af1","tid":269130,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:36:40.000Z","msg":"中立俾人屌架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da839df530edaca87c27a0b23b2c89a23fc2bb5","tid":269130,"uid":82543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中立俾人屌架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出黎屌鳩我囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bcf0f6e73f0619fa9767f4cafd6c19ccebb799","tid":269130,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:39:18.000Z","msg":"肯定唔夠ac之前隻雲狗我都未見過佢出現同我講過野，跟住又會知道話我係中立撚黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 篤爆左又換第個答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397dc793861cb96a1c23b2ef2d41492b5089690a","tid":269130,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:41:00.000Z","msg":"黎黎去去都個幾條友，on9都知中介狗啦，一話佢地就會話你蔣狗fans子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bba044873cfa62e8efcebd4e80ee4003773317","tid":269130,"uid":82543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"所以咪話2邊都傻鳩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n網絡打手又係無腦"},{"pid":"65663df73522d6adfddaf3003028974c037ee5c7","tid":269130,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以咪話2邊都傻鳩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n網絡打手又係無腦</blockquote><br />\n而家都冇再睇太撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f14750864d2caec6697959ad18725ae6dbc6c1","tid":269130,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似話醬籽追擊中介狗<br />\n都係因為私怨"},{"pid":"a1b414ba4ef5f472652a0e5355666e0630a19c0e","tid":269130,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似話醬籽追擊中介狗<br />\n都係因為私怨</blockquote><br />\n中介狗唔通有好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},